Mura Comment Spam Remover
=========================
Simple MuraCMS plugin to allow for easy removal of comment spam

INSTALLATION
============
Download as a zip file and load as a standard Mura plugin

USAGE
=====
(1) Browse to the plugin listed under the Plugins directory of your Mura Admin

(2) Click on the "Delete" link next to the unwanted comment

(3) Confirm that you want to delete the comment